Params: {3: 'Rohacchi points at his lower body. A makeshift skirt crudely fashioned out of red and yellow vinyl fabric is wrapped around his waist.'}
{3: 'Rohacchi speaks in his usual intermittent way and reaches over to remove the dress.'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "No, no, no! You can't take it off! You gotta stay in character!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'There\'s this thing written on some book before... about this "walker" guy...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "...I got it! You'll be named Rohawalker!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "Now that that's settled! Time for Martin...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "You'll be that... uhh... whatchamacallit... Marshal Martin?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "It's like being some super duper guy back in the Golden Age... I think?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "The directions it gave me were way too vague! How'd I ever find the place in such a massive area?!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Martin', 3: '...Any other info outside of the coordinates?', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "Hmmm... Lemme see... It told me to find a big ol' antenna? And in case I don't know what an antenna looks like, it even gave me a picture and all...", 4: '1'}
{3: "Ignoring Nanami's question, Martin and Rohacchi walk away."}
{3: 'Creating some distance between Nanami and themselves, Martin finally answers her question.'}
{2: 'Martin', 3: "We'll go look for it ourselves! We'll let you know if we find it!"}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "Youâ€”Wait for me! I'll go look for it too!", 4: '1'}
